These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, surfing, badminton, soccer, rugby
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, jazz, pop, soul
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
7. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Sport   | surfing | badminton | rowing | rugby | soccer |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | dubstep | jazz     | pop       | indie  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daisy, marigold, poppy, orchid
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, indie, metal, r&b, rock
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is the fan of metal##1
6. the fan of rock is the person who growsorchid##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Flower      | daisy | marigold | zinnia | poppy | orchid |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | r&b   | disco       | indie    | rock   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, fish, goat, rat
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, jet-ski, ship, subway
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Pet        | fish | goat | horse | lizard | rat |
| Transport   | bus  | boat      | subway | jet-ski | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, november, january, february, july
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, nurse, paramedic, social-worker, writer
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the writer##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the paramedic is on the far right##1
7. the writer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Birthday   | february    | march        | january | november | july |
| Job     | fisherman | social-worker | writer  | nurse   | paramedic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: banana, cherry, grapes, mango, strawberry
The people have 5 different jobs:  pilot, journalist, architect, teacher, chef
1. the teacher is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the journalist is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the architect is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the architect is in the middle##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
6. the chef is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | grapes   | banana     | cherry   | mango         | strawberry |
| Job   | pilot | teacher | architect | chef | journalist     |

