.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  chef, engineer, manager, scientist, teacher
House: gothic-revival, ranch-style, cottage, palace, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the art-deco house is on the right of the palace house##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the chef is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Job     | engineer | chef       | teacher | scientist | manager    |
| House   | palace   | art-deco | cottage  | ranch-style     | gothic-revival |

