.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, photography, woodworking
House: art-deco, futuristic, craftsman, tower, cottage
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
5. the cottage house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the futuristic house##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Hobby         | photography | camping | magic-tricks | woodworking | dancing |
| House   | craftsman       | tower   | cottage         | futuristic   | art-deco   |

