.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
There are 5 different nationalities: american, argentine, british, italian, nigerian
5 different games are played: domino, whist, mah-jongg, bridge, poker
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the british##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is the american##1
4. the italian is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
6. the person playing domino is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | italian | argentine | british | american |
| Game           | poker      | whist    | bridge  | domino     | mah-jongg     |

