.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
City: berlin, san-francisco, liverpool, hamburg, marseilles
5 different pets are kept: cat, dog, goat, rabbit, snake
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the dog is the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
7. the owner of the snake is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| City   | hamburg | berlin  | liverpool | san-francisco | marseilles |
| Pet    | dog    | rabbit | snake   | cat       | goat        |

