.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, carrot, mango, plum, spinach
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, subway, train, van, helicopter
1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person eating plum is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
5. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating plum##1
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
7. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Food    | asparagus | plum          | mango    | spinach | carrot  |
| Transport   | train  | helicopter | taxi | van | subway |

