.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, german, mexican, spanish
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, pink, lilac, grey, blood-red
1. the egyptian is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes pink is the dutch##1
4. the spanish is the person who likes lilac##1
5. the person who likes grey is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the mexican is in the middle##1
7. the mexican is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Nationality   | german | dutch      | mexican | egyptian | spanish |
| Color     | grey  | pink | lavender     | blood-red     | lilac  |

