.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, engineer, nurse, pilot, software-developer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, time-travel, adventure, comedy, spy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the software-developer is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is the nurse##1
5. the engineer is on the far right##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the nurse##1
7. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
