.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, gospel, hip-hop, house, rock
5 different pets are kept: snake, fish, dog, rat, hedgehog
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of blues##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the fan of blues##1
4. the fan of blues is the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
6. the fan of house is the owner of the dog##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | hip-hop    | rock | house   | gospel |
| Pet     | fish | snake | rat | dog | hedgehog    |

