.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, sports, time-travel
There 5 different types of food: eggplant, grapes, papaya, blueberry, carrot
1. the person eating blueberry is in the middle##1
2. the person watching action movies is the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is the person eating carrot##1
5. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
6. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
7. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | sports  | action | time-travel | romance  |
| Food         | eggplant | papaya | blueberry  | carrot    | grapes |

