.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, reggae, folk, techno, disco
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, handball, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of techno##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of techno##1
7. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | folk       | rock     | reggae  | techno  |
| Sport      | surfing | basketball | cricket | tennis | handball |

