.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, romance, satire, thriller
House: futuristic, gothic-revival, cape-cod, farmhouse, craftsman
1. the gothic-revival house is in the middle##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the futuristic house##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | thriller | romance | documentary | satire |
| House           | craftsman | farmhouse  | gothic-revival    | futuristic  | cape-cod   |

 